languages.text: "Я нахожу подозрительным, что ячейкой генокульта командовал магус. Они занимают высокое место в их иерархии, но не наивысшее... если верить имеющимся у меня донесениям".

"I find it suspicious that a Genestealer Magus was in charge of this cell. They occupy a high position in the cult power structure, but not the highest... not according to the reports I have received."

languages.text: « Je m'étonne qu'un magus des Genestealer soit à la tête de cette cellule. Cette personne occupe une position importante au sein de la hiérarchie du culte, sans en être au sommet... en tout cas, selon les rapports que j'ai reçus. »
languages.original_text: "I find it suspicious that a Genestealer Magus was in charge of this cell. They occupy a high position in the cult power structure, but not the highest... not according to the reports I have received."

traits.locale_text: « Je m'étonne qu'un psyker se soit retrouvé à la tête de cette cellule de mutants. Cela ne colle pas du tout avec les informations à ma disposition sur ce genre de secte. »

languages.text: «Resulta extraño que hubiera un Magus Genestealer a cargo de esta célula. Ocupan una posición elevada en la estructura de poder del culto, pero no la más alta... no según los informes que me han llegado».
languages.original_text: "I find it suspicious that a Genestealer Magus was in charge of this cell. They occupy a high position in the cult power structure, but not the highest... not according to the reports I have received."

languages.text: 「ジーンスティーラーのメイガスが、この独房の責任者であったことは疑わしいです。彼らは魔女団の権力構造の中で高い地位にいますが、最高位ではありません…少なくとも、私が受け取った報告によれば」
languages.original_text: "I find it suspicious that a Genestealer Magus was in charge of this cell. They occupy a high position in the cult power structure, but not the highest... not according to the reports I have received."

traits.locale_text: 「異能者が変異体細胞を管理していたとは疑わしい。これは…この種の魔女団のデータと一致しないんだ」

languages.text: “区区一位教团教主，竟然统治着整支基因窃取者教派，这相当可疑。诚然，教团教主确实有着尊崇的地位，但绝对不是教派的最高领袖……至少根据我收到的那些报告来看，并非如此。”
languages.original_text: "I find it suspicious that a Genestealer Magus was in charge of this cell. They occupy a high position in the cult power structure, but not the highest... not according to the reports I have received."

traits.locale_text: “灵能者担任变种人教派的头目，这相当可疑。这种情况……与我所知的此类邪教的特点完全不符。”

languages.original_text: "I find it suspicious that a Genestealer Magus was in charge of this cell. They occupy a high position in the cult power structure, but not the highest... not according to the reports I have received."
